name: Nature Vs Tech V2
description:
Nature Vs Tech is a tower defense game made over 48 hours for the Adelaide AIE Game Jam by Max Winzar, Daniel Hood and Kaleb Ryan. The build uploaded is in a beta state but playable and showcases our work.

UPDATE: The build is now in a playable state, however you may still run into bugs and issues. Please enjoy and sorry for the wait!
